name: follow me
description: A popular influencer and his friends travel the world and film themselves in extreme situations. In Russia, they are invited to a mysterious escape room by an eccentric millionaire and see a given video success on social media in front of them. But no likes in the world can buy them free from the nightmare that awaits

name: tenet
description: Christopher Nolan's 'Tenet' is an epic action film that takes its starting point in the international spy world.John David Washington stars as the 'protagonist' in Christopher Nolan's new action film 'The Ten.' In a shadowy world of espionage at a high international level, the word Tenet is the only tool he has to save humanity. His goals are developed while the mission is being performed. Beyond time. Not time travel. Inversion.

name: Come Play
description: Oliver is a lonely young guy who does not feel like anyone else. He longs to have a real friend and seeks comfort and refuge in his mobile phone and tablet, his two constant companions. When a mysterious creature uses Oliver's devices against him to break into our world, Oliver's parents must fight to save their son from the monster behind the screen

name: trolls 2: world tour
description: Poppy and Kvist embark on an adventure that will take them far beyond the reality they previously knew. During the journey, they will discover that they belong to just one of the six different kinds of wizards who live scattered over six different countries and who are dedicated to six different kinds of music: Funk, Country, Techno, Classical, Pop and Rock. Their world will be much bigger, and much louder, than before.

name: online
description: Kate Mitchell is a bit of a creative lone wolf. When she is admitted to the school she has always dreamed of, she immediately wants to fly there. But her dad, Rick, gets a better idea. He wants to gather the whole family one last time and together drive Katie to school. Her bubbly mother Linda, their chubby dog ​​Monchi and her playful little brother Aaron will also come along.

name: honest thief
description: Liam Neeson is the bank robber Tom Carter, who has long eluded the police with his smart safe drawers. When he suddenly meets the woman in his life, he makes the decision to hand over himself and all the stolen millions to the police. The goal is to get a deal for a shorter sentence and then be able to start a new life in earnest. But Tom soon realizes that the police are more corrupt than he is, and to clear his name he has to fight back.

name: the woman in the window
description: Anna Fox lives alone in an apartment in New York where she spends her days drinking wine, watching old movies ... and spying on her neighbors. When the Russell family moves across the street, they first appear as the perfect family. But when Anna looks out the window one evening, she sees something she should not

name: pinocchio
description: In this new live-action interpretation of the classic Italian saga, we once again get to know the wood carver Geppetto, whose wooden doll Pinocchio is brought to life under magical circumstances. The gullible Pinocchio is easily misled, which takes him on an adventurous journey filled with magical creatures and fantastic spectacles among friends and enemies. However, the dream of becoming a real boy can only be realized if he starts listening to his father once and for all.

name: operation north pole
description: Fjällräven Swifty works in the mail room at ABDS mail handling, but he has much bigger dreams. He wants to be someone other than a mountain fox that blends into the surroundings: He wants to be an iron jerk, one of the cool and famous husky couriers.

name: pelle kanin 2
description: Bea, Thomas and the rabbits have created a functioning family, but no matter how hard Pelle tries, he cannot get rid of his reputation as a troublemaker. He then embarks on an adventure outside the garden's safe wall and ends up in a world where his mischievous antics are actually appreciated. But when his family risks everything to come and get him home, Pelle has to think through what kind of rabbit he really wants to be.
